[
  {
    "line_start": 22,
    "line_end": 22,
    "text": "这两人就是五行双杀。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 24,
    "line_end": 24,
    "text": "哼。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 32,
    "line_end": 32,
    "text": "他是金木水火，我是土。我简直是条土驴，是个土豆，是只土狗。",
    "speaker_name": "泥人"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 40,
    "line_end": 40,
    "text": "就算我们不认得傅大侠，也该认得出这柄刀的。",
    "speaker_name": "泥人"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 42,
    "line_end": 42,
    "text": "可是我们也想不到傅大侠会帮着他出手。",
    "speaker_name": "木头人"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 44,
    "line_end": 44,
    "text": "他这条命已是我的。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 46,
    "line_end": 46,
    "text": "是。",
    "speaker_name": "木头人"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 48,
    "line_end": 48,
    "text": "除了我之外，谁也不能伤他毫发。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 50,
    "text": "是。",
    "speaker_name": "木头人"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 52,
    "line_end": 52,
    "text": "只要傅大侠肯饶了我这条狗命，我立刻就滚得远远的。",
    "speaker_name": "泥人"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 54,
    "line_end": 54,
    "text": "滚。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 58,
    "line_end": 58,
    "text": "我知道你决不会杀他们。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 60,
    "line_end": 60,
    "text": "哦？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 62,
    "line_end": 62,
    "text": "因为他们还不配。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 70,
    "line_end": 70,
    "text": "我听说过，他们杀了石霸天，代价是十三万两。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 72,
    "line_end": 72,
    "text": "完全正确。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 74,
    "line_end": 74,
    "text": "你的命当然比石霸天值钱些。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 76,
    "line_end": 76,
    "text": "值钱得多。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 78,
    "line_end": 78,
    "text": "能出得起这种重价，要他们来杀你的人却不多。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 82,
    "line_end": 82,
    "text": "你没有问，只因为你早已知道这个人是谁。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 88,
    "line_end": 88,
    "text": "你的未了心愿，就是为了要对付这个人？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 90,
    "line_end": 90,
    "text": "你已问得太多！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 92,
    "line_end": 92,
    "text": "你不说？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 94,
    "line_end": 94,
    "text": "不说。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 96,
    "line_end": 96,
    "text": "那么你走！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 98,
    "line_end": 98,
    "text": "更不能走！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 100,
    "line_end": 100,
    "text": "莫忘记我借给你一年，这一年时光，就是你欠我的。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 102,
    "line_end": 102,
    "text": "你要我还？怎么还？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 104,
    "line_end": 104,
    "text": "去做完你该做的事。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 106,
    "line_end": 106,
    "text": "可是我……",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 108,
    "line_end": 108,
    "text": "你若真是个男子汉，就算要死，也得死得光明磊落。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 114,
    "line_end": 114,
    "text": "你的剑还在，你人也未死，你为什么不敢去？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 116,
    "line_end": 116,
    "text": "好，我去。可是一年之后，我必再来。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 118,
    "line_end": 118,
    "text": "我知道！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 122,
    "line_end": 122,
    "text": "你还是不喝？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 124,
    "line_end": 124,
    "text": "不喝！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 126,
    "line_end": 126,
    "text": "不喝酒的人，真的能永远清醒？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 128,
    "line_end": 128,
    "text": "未必。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 148,
    "line_end": 148,
    "text": "你是我的影子？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 152,
    "line_end": 152,
    "text": "不是。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 154,
    "line_end": 154,
    "text": "你为什么跟着我？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 156,
    "line_end": 156,
    "text": "因为我不愿让你死在别人手里。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 158,
    "line_end": 158,
    "text": "不必你费心，我一向能照顾自己。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 160,
    "line_end": 160,
    "text": "你真的能？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 164,
    "line_end": 164,
    "text": "只有真正无情的人，才能照顾自己，你却太多情。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 166,
    "line_end": 166,
    "text": "你呢？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 168,
    "line_end": 168,
    "text": "我纵然有情，也已忘了，忘了很久。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 174,
    "line_end": 174,
    "text": "你若真的认为你已能照顾自己，你也错了。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 176,
    "line_end": 176,
    "text": "哦？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 178,
    "line_end": 178,
    "text": "这世上至少还有一个人能伤害你。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 180,
    "line_end": 180,
    "text": "谁？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 182,
    "text": "你自己。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 194,
    "line_end": 194,
    "text": "你想不到？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 196,
    "line_end": 196,
    "text": "我想不到，你却早已知道！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 198,
    "line_end": 198,
    "text": "哦？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 200,
    "line_end": 200,
    "text": "你早巳知道这地方已成死镇，所以才会带着你的酒乐歌伎一起来。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 204,
    "line_end": 204,
    "text": "你当然也知道这地方是怎么会变成这样子的。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 206,
    "line_end": 206,
    "text": "我当然知道！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 208,
    "line_end": 208,
    "text": "是为了什么？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 210,
    "line_end": 210,
    "text": "是为了我。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 212,
    "line_end": 212,
    "text": "是为了你？你怎么会将一个繁荣的市镇变为坟墓？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 236,
    "line_end": 236,
    "text": "你赶路很急，是为了什么？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 238,
    "line_end": 238,
    "text": "我要赶去奔丧。",
    "speaker_name": "骑士"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 240,
    "line_end": 240,
    "text": "是不是你的亲人死了？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 242,
    "line_end": 242,
    "text": "是我的二叔。",
    "speaker_name": "骑士"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 244,
    "line_end": 244,
    "text": "你赶去后，能不能救活他？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 248,
    "line_end": 248,
    "text": "既然不能，你又何必赶得这么急？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 250,
    "line_end": 250,
    "text": "你究竟要什么？",
    "speaker_name": "骑士"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 254,
    "line_end": 254,
    "text": "我要买你这匹马。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 256,
    "line_end": 256,
    "text": "我不卖！",
    "speaker_name": "骑士"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 258,
    "line_end": 258,
    "text": "你卖不卖？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 260,
    "line_end": 260,
    "text": "人死不能复生，我又何必急着要赶去。",
    "speaker_name": "骑士"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 264,
    "line_end": 264,
    "text": "我知道我甩不脱你，可是现在我已有六条腿。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 270,
    "line_end": 270,
    "text": "再见，一年后再见！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 280,
    "line_end": 280,
    "text": "我知道你一向很少拔刀。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 282,
    "line_end": 282,
    "text": "嗯。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 284,
    "line_end": 284,
    "text": "你的刀不是给人看的。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 286,
    "line_end": 286,
    "text": "嗯。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 288,
    "line_end": 288,
    "text": "这一次你为什么要无故拔刀？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 288,
    "line_end": 288,
    "text": "因为你的腿。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 290,
    "line_end": 290,
    "text": "我的腿？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 292,
    "line_end": 292,
    "text": "你没有六条腿。只要一上这匹马，你就没有腿了，连一条腿都没有。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 338,
    "line_end": 338,
    "text": "只恨我生得太晚，我没有见过！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 340,
    "line_end": 340,
    "text": "你没见到过叶开的刀？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 342,
    "line_end": 342,
    "text": "只恨我无缘，我……",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 344,
    "line_end": 344,
    "text": "你无缘，却有幸。以前也有人见到他的刀出手……",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 346,
    "line_end": 346,
    "text": "现在那些人都已死了？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 350,
    "line_end": 350,
    "text": "就算他们人未死，心却已死。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 352,
    "line_end": 352,
    "text": "心已死？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 354,
    "line_end": 354,
    "text": "无论谁，只要见过他的刀出手，终身不敢用刀。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 356,
    "line_end": 356,
    "text": "可是他用的是飞刀！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 358,
    "line_end": 358,
    "text": "飞刀也是刀。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 364,
    "line_end": 364,
    "text": "你用过刀？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 366,
    "line_end": 366,
    "text": "没有。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 368,
    "line_end": 368,
    "text": "你见过多少真正会用刀的人？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 370,
    "line_end": 370,
    "text": "没有几个。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 372,
    "line_end": 372,
    "text": "那么你根本不配谈论刀。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 374,
    "line_end": 374,
    "text": "也许我不配谈论刀，也许你的刀法并不是天下无双的刀法，我都不能确定。我只能确定一件事。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 376,
    "line_end": 376,
    "text": "什么事？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 378,
    "line_end": 378,
    "text": "现在我又有了六条腿，你却只有两条。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 416,
    "line_end": 416,
    "text": "你终于还是追来了。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 418,
    "line_end": 418,
    "text": "嗯。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 420,
    "line_end": 420,
    "text": "无论你想盯住什么人，那个人是不是都一定跑不了？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 422,
    "line_end": 422,
    "text": "嗯。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 424,
    "line_end": 424,
    "text": "幸好我不是女人，否则岂非也要被你盯得死死的，想不嫁给你都不行。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 474,
    "line_end": 474,
    "text": "我现在才明白，你这把刀除了杀人之外还有什么用！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 476,
    "line_end": 476,
    "text": "哦？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 478,
    "line_end": 478,
    "text": "你还会用来吓孩子。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 480,
    "line_end": 480,
    "text": "我只吓一种孩子。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 482,
    "line_end": 482,
    "text": "哪种？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 484,
    "line_end": 484,
    "text": "杀人的孩子！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 496,
    "line_end": 496,
    "text": "你就是鬼外婆？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 498,
    "line_end": 498,
    "text": "想不到你居然也知道我。",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 500,
    "line_end": 500,
    "text": "你当然也知道我有种习惯。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 502,
    "line_end": 502,
    "text": "什么习惯？",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 504,
    "line_end": 504,
    "text": "我从不杀女人。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 506,
    "line_end": 506,
    "text": "这是种好习惯。",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 510,
    "line_end": 510,
    "text": "你虽然老了，毕竟也是个女人。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 512,
    "line_end": 512,
    "text": "只可惜你没有见过我年轻的时候，否则……",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 514,
    "line_end": 514,
    "text": "否则我还是要杀你！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 516,
    "line_end": 516,
    "text": "我记得你好像刚才还说过，从不杀女人的。",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 518,
    "line_end": 518,
    "text": "你是例外。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 520,
    "line_end": 520,
    "text": "为什么我要例外？",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 522,
    "line_end": 522,
    "text": "孩子们是纯洁无辜的，你不该利用他们，害了他们一生。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 524,
    "line_end": 524,
    "text": "好外婆喜欢孩子，孩子们也喜欢替好外婆做事，跟你有什么关系？",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 532,
    "line_end": 532,
    "text": "别人怕你的蔷薇剑，我……",
    "speaker_name": "鬼外婆"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 550,
    "line_end": 550,
    "text": "这次你又没有看错。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 552,
    "line_end": 552,
    "text": "我很少错。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 554,
    "line_end": 554,
    "text": "但孩子们还是无辜的，他们一定也从小就被鬼外婆拐出来……",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 562,
    "line_end": 562,
    "text": "她一定用尽了各种法子，从小就让那些孩子学会仇恨和罪恶。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 564,
    "line_end": 564,
    "text": "所以你本不该放她走的。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 566,
    "line_end": 566,
    "text": "我想不到她那包糖糕里竟藏着江南霹雳堂的火器。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 568,
    "line_end": 568,
    "text": "你应该想得到。糕里既然可能有五毒钉，就可能有霹雳子！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 570,
    "line_end": 570,
    "text": "你早已想到？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 574,
    "line_end": 574,
    "text": "你既然也认为不该放她走，为什么不出手。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 576,
    "line_end": 576,
    "text": "因为她要杀的不是我，也因为想不到你会这么蠢。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 578,
    "line_end": 578,
    "text": "也许不是我太蠢，而是你太精！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 580,
    "line_end": 580,
    "text": "哦？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 582,
    "line_end": 582,
    "text": "直到现在我还不明白，那烟中的毒雾，鞍里的毒蛇，你是怎么看出来的。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 584,
    "line_end": 584,
    "text": "杀人的法子有很多种，暗杀也是其中一种；而且是最为可怕的一种。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 586,
    "line_end": 586,
    "text": "我知道！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 588,
    "line_end": 588,
    "text": "你知不知道暗杀的法子又有多少种？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 592,
    "line_end": 592,
    "text": "不知道！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 594,
    "line_end": 594,
    "text": "你知不知道这三百年来，有多少不该死的人被暗杀而死？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 596,
    "line_end": 596,
    "text": "不知道！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 598,
    "line_end": 598,
    "text": "至少有五百三十八个人。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 600,
    "line_end": 600,
    "text": "你算过？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 602,
    "line_end": 602,
    "text": "我算过，整整费了我七年时光才算清楚。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 604,
    "line_end": 604,
    "text": "你为什么要费这么大功夫，去算这些事？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 606,
    "line_end": 606,
    "text": "因为我若没有去算过，现在至少已死了十次，你也已死了三次。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 610,
    "line_end": 610,
    "text": "我说的这五百三十八人，本都是武林中的一流高手，杀他们的人，本不是他们的对手。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 612,
    "line_end": 612,
    "text": "只不过这些人杀人的法子都很恶毒巧妙，所以才能得手。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 614,
    "line_end": 614,
    "text": "被暗杀而死的虽有五百三十八人，杀他们的刺客却只有四百八十三个。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 616,
    "line_end": 616,
    "text": "因为他们当中有些是死在同一人之手的。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 618,
    "line_end": 618,
    "text": "这些刺客杀人的法子，也有些是相同的。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 620,
    "line_end": 620,
    "text": "我想得到。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 622,
    "line_end": 622,
    "text": "他们一共只用了两百二十七种法子。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 626,
    "line_end": 626,
    "text": "这两百二十七种暗杀的法子，当然都是最恶毒、最巧妙的。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 628,
    "line_end": 628,
    "text": "当然。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 630,
    "line_end": 630,
    "text": "你知道其中多少种？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 632,
    "line_end": 632,
    "text": "两百二十七种。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 634,
    "line_end": 634,
    "text": "这些法子我本来连一种都不懂！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 636,
    "line_end": 636,
    "text": "现在你至少知道三种。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 638,
    "line_end": 638,
    "text": "不止三种！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 640,
    "line_end": 640,
    "text": "不止？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 642,
    "line_end": 642,
    "text": "你知不知道这半年来我已被人暗杀过多少次？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 646,
    "line_end": 646,
    "text": "不算你见过的，也有三十九次。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 648,
    "line_end": 648,
    "text": "他们用的法子都不同？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 650,
    "line_end": 650,
    "text": "非但完全不同，而且都是我想不到的，可是我直到现在还活着。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 688,
    "line_end": 688,
    "text": "你在想什么？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 690,
    "line_end": 690,
    "text": "我在想人，两个人。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 692,
    "line_end": 692,
    "text": "你想的这两个人里面，有没有一个是我？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 694,
    "line_end": 694,
    "text": "没有。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 696,
    "line_end": 696,
    "text": "两个人都不是你。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 698,
    "line_end": 698,
    "text": "不是我，是谁？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 702,
    "line_end": 702,
    "text": "一个是傅红雪。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 704,
    "line_end": 704,
    "text": "傅红雪？就是在凤凰集上等着你的那个人？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 706,
    "line_end": 706,
    "text": "嗯。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 708,
    "line_end": 708,
    "text": "他是你的仇人？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 710,
    "line_end": 710,
    "text": "不是。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 712,
    "line_end": 712,
    "text": "是你的朋友？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 714,
    "line_end": 714,
    "text": "也不是。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 716,
    "line_end": 716,
    "text": "你永远想不到他为什么要在凤凰集等着我的。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 718,
    "line_end": 718,
    "text": "他在等着杀我。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 720,
    "line_end": 720,
    "text": "可是他并没有杀你。",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 722,
    "line_end": 722,
    "text": "非但没有杀我，而且还救了我三次。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 724,
    "line_end": 724,
    "text": "你们这种男人做的事，我们女人好像永远也不会懂的。",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 726,
    "line_end": 726,
    "text": "你们本来就不懂。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 728,
    "line_end": 728,
    "text": "你想的还有一个人是谁？",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 730,
    "line_end": 730,
    "text": "是个我想杀的人。只可惜我自己也知道，我永远也杀不了他的。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 736,
    "line_end": 736,
    "text": "你该睡了，我也该走了。",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 738,
    "line_end": 738,
    "text": "你走！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 740,
    "line_end": 740,
    "text": "我知道你现在的心情。我本该留下来陪你的，可是……",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 742,
    "line_end": 742,
    "text": "可是你非走不可，因为虽然在风尘中，你这里却从不留客，能让我睡在这里，已经很给我面子。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 744,
    "line_end": 744,
    "text": "也许我本不该留你，也许你本不该来的。",
    "speaker_name": "明月心"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 756,
    "line_end": 756,
    "text": "傅红雪，傅红雪，你为什么会是这样的人？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 766,
    "line_end": 766,
    "text": "外面在下雨，下得很大。",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 768,
    "line_end": 768,
    "text": "我知道！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 770,
    "line_end": 770,
    "text": "你本不该出来的！",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 772,
    "line_end": 772,
    "text": "你可以在外面淋雨。我为什么不可以？",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 774,
    "line_end": 774,
    "text": "你可以？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 780,
    "line_end": 780,
    "text": "我当然可以淋雨，任何人都有淋雨的自由。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 784,
    "line_end": 784,
    "text": "但我却不是特地出来淋雨的！",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 790,
    "line_end": 790,
    "text": "你出来干什么？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 792,
    "line_end": 792,
    "text": "我想告诉你一件事，一个秘密。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 794,
    "line_end": 794,
    "text": "现在你已准备告诉我？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 798,
    "line_end": 798,
    "text": "你本来岂非宁死也不肯说的？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 800,
    "line_end": 800,
    "text": "我本来的确已下了决心，决不告诉任何人。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 802,
    "line_end": 802,
    "text": "现在你为什么要告诉我？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 804,
    "line_end": 804,
    "text": "现在我告诉你，只因为我忽然发现了一件事。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 806,
    "line_end": 806,
    "text": "什么事？",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪"
  },
  {
    "line_start": 808,
    "line_end": 808,
    "text": "你不是人，根本就不是。",
    "speaker_name": "燕南飞"
  }
]